&lt;p&gt;Pippin Title is a venture-backed real estate tech startup that offers nationwide, comprehensive, high-quality, technology-driven title search services to clients across the US. We’re bringing title search into the 21st century.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pippin is headquartered in New York City. With a remote-first culture, we look to hire the best talent wherever they are located across the country.&lt;/p&gt;
