&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Customer Success Manager who will build meaningful relationships with our current clients and drive Pippin’s long-term sales growth strategy. As part of the Customer Success team, you will work closely with the Sales team and CEO to: 1) drive and iterate a seamless onboarding process for new clients, 2) leverage Pippin’s expertise to help current clients solve their business problems, 3) grow our share of wallet, and 4) ensure the long-term success of our client to reduce churn.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While Customer Success is part of the Revenue team, it will also work closely with the customer service and operations teams. At the moment, there will not be a supervisory component to this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
