&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage sustainable, seamless, and effective onboarding processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to inbound customer requests and focus on scaling interesting clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the sales team to transition prospects to clients smoothly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an advocate for current Pippin clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regularly consult current clients to understand their pain points and propose solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grow Pippin’s share of wallet through relationship-based sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand and effectively educate clients about Pippin’s product and technology pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute effective engagement strategies for current clients such as creating or proposing marketing materials related to the client experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propose and research new products or services to maximize client satisfaction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help manage revenue technology stack such as Hubspot and integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather, synthesize, and report on key client metrics&lt;/li&gt;
